item.title: CVE-2017-8166|2024-09-17T00:11:37.849Z -- huawei%20technologies%20co.%2C%20ltd. -- honor%20v9
item.description: Huawei mobile phones Honor V9 with the software versions before Duke-AL20C00B195 have an App Lock bypass vulnerability. An attacker could perform specific operations to bypass the App Lock to use apps on a target mobile phone.
